接口 Connector

  • 所有已知实现类:
    ConnectorAdapter, MockConnector, NioConnector

    public interface Connector
    Connector which used to communicate between nodes internally.

    2022-03-31

      • initialize

        void initialize()
        Initialize the connector.

        Should not call more than once.

      • sendRequestVote

        void sendRequestVote(@Nonnull
                     RequestVoteRpc rpc,
                     @Nonnull
                     Collection<NodeEndpoint> destinationEndpoints)
        Send RequestVote RPC.

        Remember to exclude self node before sending.

        Do nothing if destination endpoints is empty.

        参数:
        rpc - rpc
        destinationEndpoints - destination endpoints
